{"tid":1213993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會今日不開會","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:16:07.000Z","uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a19dd337397abb2e181033e288cf506247f316cb","tid":1213993,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"原定於周三舉行的立法會大會中，將會就《逃犯條例》修訂進行二讀，惟在數以萬計市民包圍下，最終決定暫停，立法會秘書處周四（6月13日）早上11時公佈，今日會議取消，而大批市民因未能進入立法會示威區而與警員中信天橋對峙。《果燃台》直擊現場最新狀況。"},{"pid":"a72d51b8471bb3a1a8d31b251aa64483e378d720","tid":1213993,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190613&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59709258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190613%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59709258&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=0858fd75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190613%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59709258&h=9746a697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190613&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59709258</a>"}]}